GDN Charlene is a High Quality Character for Genesis 3 Female

DAZ Studio Iray and 3DelightSSS based Materials 
Attention the IRAY Shaders are created for DAZ Studio 4.9 and Higher only!

The Following products are required in order to use GDN Charlene for Genesis 3 Female:
Genesis 3 Female: Included with DAZ Studio 4+
Genesis 3 Female Head Morphs: http://www.daz3d.com/genesis-3-female-head-morphs

Body Morph and Extra's such as Nipples, Breast Cleavage, Smaller Navel, Smaller Waist and Genitalia Are all custom Sculpted in Zbrush
The head morph is mainly Custom sculpted in zbrush and partly DAZ Dialed with the Genesis 3 Female Head Morphs
